00:01:08.940 --> 00:01:11.500
Before we integrated
Play Billing,

00:01:11.500 --> 00:01:14.330
our subscription process
took around two minutes.

00:01:14.330 --> 00:01:16.090
And we were asking
our users to fill out

00:01:16.090 --> 00:01:18.560
a series of forms,
all on their phone.

00:01:18.560 --> 00:01:21.240
And now with Play Billing,
because the user has a credit

00:01:21.240 --> 00:01:24.890
card or their Paypal information
associated with their account,

00:01:24.890 --> 00:01:26.900
the user can subscribe
to "The New York Times"

00:01:26.900 --> 00:01:28.280
within two taps.

00:01:28.280 --> 00:01:30.720
Some of the tap features I
really like about Play Billing

00:01:30.720 --> 00:01:33.310
