enable local currency

00:01:33.310 --> 00:01:35.370
billing in over 50 countries.

00:01:35.370 --> 00:01:38.270
And, two, it was very
easy to add a free trial.

00:01:38.270 --> 00:01:40.680
With Play Billing,
we're able to realize

00:01:40.680 --> 00:01:45.134
